1
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,180
=My Name is Zhao Chuxi=

2
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:05,180
=Episode 23=

3
00:01:06,030 --> 00:01:06,870
I hereby announce,

4
00:01:07,230 --> 00:01:08,820
in accordance with the Board's bylaws,

5
00:01:09,380 --> 00:01:10,950
11 members attended the meeting,

6
00:01:11,070 --> 00:01:13,430
four voted in favor, and seven opposed.

7
00:01:13,540 --> 00:01:15,710
The votes don't exceed 50%
of the voting rights

8
00:01:15,710 --> 00:01:17,740
stipulated in the bylaws.

9
00:01:18,070 --> 00:01:21,820
Zhao Chuxi will remain as chairman.

10
00:01:22,710 --> 00:01:23,550
Du Xinan!

11
00:01:24,310 --> 00:01:25,590
How dare you set me up!

12
00:01:25,740 --> 00:01:26,900
Why are you doing this?

13
00:01:30,380 --> 00:01:31,460
Her kindness to me

14
00:01:31,980 --> 00:01:33,430
will never be forgotten.

15
00:01:35,740 --> 00:01:38,870
(These eight words can explain)

16
00:01:38,980 --> 00:01:41,590
(what kind of person moderate Du Xinan is.)

17
00:01:41,870 --> 00:01:43,790
(You could say he's inflexible and rigid.)

18
00:01:43,900 --> 00:01:45,540
(Or you could call him loyal to a fault.)

19
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,270
(Perhaps it's more accurate to say)

20
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,740
(Du Xinan doesn't support Zhao Chuxi)

21
00:01:48,740 --> 00:01:50,670
(because of Zhao Chuxi himself.)

22
00:01:51,030 --> 00:01:53,870
(The person whom he supported)

23
00:01:53,980 --> 00:01:55,380
(has always been one, Ms. Jian.)

24
00:02:05,030 --> 00:02:05,870
Mr. Du.

25
00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:09,740
This is what I promised Ms. Jian.

26
00:02:12,430 --> 00:02:13,270
I hereby announce,

27
00:02:14,900 --> 00:02:16,610
the Board Meeting is officially concluded.

28
00:02:17,060 --> 00:02:18,150
I'll arrange a venue

29
00:02:18,830 --> 00:02:20,200
to host everyone for a gathering.

30
00:02:20,660 --> 00:02:22,740
I hope you can all join me.

31
00:02:25,020 --> 00:02:28,500
(Sanjiang Group)

32
00:02:28,500 --> 00:02:30,940
(Zhao Chuxi successfully
takes over Sanjiang Group.)

33
00:02:31,550 --> 00:02:33,150
(After the Board Meeting is concluded,)

34
00:02:33,390 --> 00:02:34,710
(everyone finally realized)

35
00:02:34,940 --> 00:02:37,220
(they had all been played by Du Xinan.)

36
00:02:47,430 --> 00:02:48,320
Mr. Zhao.

37
00:02:48,340 --> 00:02:49,620
Everyone has already arrived.

38
00:02:49,740 --> 00:02:51,510
They've been waiting upstairs for a while.

39
00:02:51,780 --> 00:02:54,620
I didn't expect everyone to show up.

40
00:02:55,830 --> 00:02:58,030
They dare miss Aunt Jian's family dinner.

41
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:59,460
But they all came to my banquet.

42
00:03:00,010 --> 00:03:01,390
They're showing me respect?

43
00:03:01,390 --> 00:03:03,900
Maybe someone was unhappy with the meeting,

44
00:03:04,220 --> 00:03:05,530
so they're here to cause trouble.

45
00:03:05,530 --> 00:03:06,420
Let's go.

46
00:03:06,430 --> 00:03:07,940
We'll confront them head-on.

47
00:03:15,830 --> 00:03:16,670
Du Xinan,

48
00:03:17,150 --> 00:03:19,030
don't you want to explain to us

49
00:03:19,030 --> 00:03:20,740
why you agreed to Zhao Chuxi

50
00:03:20,740 --> 00:03:21,900
becoming the chairman?

51
00:03:23,220 --> 00:03:24,430
What?

52
00:03:24,550 --> 00:03:27,430
Do you have some unspeakable deal

53
00:03:27,430 --> 00:03:29,150
with Zhao Chuxi?

54
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:33,180
Ms. Jian just passed away.

55
00:03:33,710 --> 00:03:36,060
Instead of protecting her business,

56
00:03:36,270 --> 00:03:38,990
you're fighting for power and profit.

57
00:03:39,990 --> 00:03:41,030
How absurd.

58
00:03:41,270 --> 00:03:42,110
Du Xinan,

59
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:44,870
we don't like hearing those words.

60
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:46,180
Ms. Jian has passed away.

61
00:03:46,660 --> 00:03:48,870
We've followed her for years.

62
00:03:49,150 --> 00:03:51,390
Naturally, we'll support her successor.

63
00:03:51,390 --> 00:03:53,180
Otherwise, why are we even here?

64
00:03:55,150 --> 00:03:57,550
Mr. He's stance is exactly my stance.

65
00:03:58,150 --> 00:03:59,310
So we'll support him.

66
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:01,390
It means the same thing anyway.

67
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:02,780
However,

68
00:04:03,430 --> 00:04:04,900
Ms. Jian just passed away recently.

69
00:04:05,550 --> 00:04:07,310
The company is now facing major crises.

70
00:04:07,740 --> 00:04:09,220
But precisely because of this,

71
00:04:10,550 --> 00:04:11,830
we need to stick together.

72
00:04:14,270 --> 00:04:17,860
Zhao Chuxi is Ms. Jian's chosen successor.

73
00:04:20,300 --> 00:04:21,390
But, Du,

74
00:04:22,300 --> 00:04:23,300
tell me

75
00:04:23,980 --> 00:04:26,100
if you are really willing to let

76
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:27,390
this newcomer to the company,

77
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:28,390
who knows nothing,

78
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:29,630
has no experience at all,

79
00:04:29,630 --> 00:04:30,750
just a young and green kid,

80
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:32,420
start giving us orders, huh?

81
00:04:32,630 --> 00:04:34,420
You might be fine with it, but we aren't.

82
00:04:34,630 --> 00:04:36,630
Why should we entrust our future

83
00:04:36,780 --> 00:04:37,750
to Zhao Chuxi?

84
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:42,590
Mr. Zhao is here.

85
00:04:44,150 --> 00:04:45,900
Apologies, I'm late.

86
00:04:46,100 --> 00:04:47,780
Traffic jam. Sorry to keep you waiting.

87
00:04:48,150 --> 00:04:49,220
Please, have a seat.

88
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:52,190
Being early or late doesn't matter.

89
00:04:52,590 --> 00:04:53,780
It's great that you're here.

90
00:04:54,190 --> 00:04:55,860
Today is a great opportunity.

91
00:04:56,460 --> 00:04:59,030
It's been a while since we gathered together.

92
00:04:59,780 --> 00:05:00,750
Normally,

93
00:05:01,030 --> 00:05:02,190
we're all too busy.

94
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:03,750
We should

95
00:05:04,420 --> 00:05:05,460
thank you for that.

96
00:05:05,710 --> 00:05:07,030
Mr. He, no need to be so polite.

97
00:05:07,150 --> 00:05:08,510
This is what I should do.

98
00:05:08,830 --> 00:05:09,830
Zhao Chuxi,

99
00:05:09,980 --> 00:05:11,750
sitting in this position isn't easy.

100
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:12,950
Some people

101
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:15,300
should weigh their capabilities carefully.

102
00:05:17,590 --> 00:05:18,590
Zhao Chuxi,

103
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:22,300
do you know how dangerous this position is?

104
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:26,030
You're responsible for others' livelihoods.

105
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:31,070
It could even put your life at risk.

106
00:05:41,070 --> 00:05:41,910
I understand.

107
00:05:42,660 --> 00:05:44,420
Everyone here is a senior at the company.

108
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:46,540
The advice you're giving

109
00:05:46,710 --> 00:05:48,150
is tough but well-meaning.

110
00:05:48,710 --> 00:05:50,540
I just took over the company.

111
00:05:50,540 --> 00:05:52,130
There's still so much I need to learn.

112
00:05:52,150 --> 00:05:55,750
I hope all of you can guide and support me.

113
00:05:57,420 --> 00:05:59,100
You speak quite well.

114
00:06:10,030 --> 00:06:10,870
Today,

115
00:06:11,100 --> 00:06:14,070
I gather everyone here not just for dinner.

116
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:16,980
I want to discuss something with you all.

117
00:06:17,300 --> 00:06:18,860
Since I recently took over the company,

118
00:06:19,100 --> 00:06:21,420
I'm lacking experience and feel overwhelmed.

119
00:06:21,590 --> 00:06:23,220
I'm sincerely hoping

120
00:06:23,510 --> 00:06:25,630
that you seniors can help me.

121
00:06:27,300 --> 00:06:28,140
Chuxi,

122
00:06:28,710 --> 00:06:30,070
we want to help you too.

123
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:32,030
But you're just too young.

124
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:34,340
Let me be blunt.

125
00:06:35,190 --> 00:06:36,030
Zhao Chuxi,

126
00:06:36,350 --> 00:06:38,900
none of us really trust you.

127
00:06:52,030 --> 00:06:52,870
Fine.

128
00:06:53,630 --> 00:06:55,300
I'll be straightforward too.

129
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:59,420
Ms. Jian gave me this position.

130
00:06:59,540 --> 00:07:00,390
I know

131
00:07:00,980 --> 00:07:02,710
you all think I'm unqualified.

132
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:04,230
Honestly, so do I.

133
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:06,150
When Ms. Jian first told me about this,

134
00:07:06,980 --> 00:07:08,030
I was confused too.

135
00:07:08,710 --> 00:07:10,780
I was scared. I felt I lacked the ability.

136
00:07:10,950 --> 00:07:13,220
Afraid I'd ruin this big company.

137
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:15,590
In the past,

138
00:07:17,030 --> 00:07:17,980
if I was put

139
00:07:18,340 --> 00:07:19,660
in a luxurious place like this,

140
00:07:19,900 --> 00:07:21,400
I wouldn't have even dared to dream.

141
00:07:22,030 --> 00:07:25,900
Even today, I feel it's a waste of money.

142
00:07:26,950 --> 00:07:27,860
Ms. Jian once said,

143
00:07:28,030 --> 00:07:29,780
I'm an ordinary guy without ambition.

144
00:07:30,030 --> 00:07:32,300
It's true. What I just want is some money,

145
00:07:32,780 --> 00:07:36,150
a wife, a car, and returning home proudly.

146
00:07:36,150 --> 00:07:37,750
I can offer you five million right now.

147
00:07:38,220 --> 00:07:39,980
Take the money and leave this position.

148
00:07:40,980 --> 00:07:41,830
Can you do that?

149
00:07:43,420 --> 00:07:44,750
What a joke.

150
00:07:46,220 --> 00:07:48,190
If you'd said this to me a week ago,

151
00:07:48,770 --> 00:07:51,100
I would've agreed without hesitation.

152
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:53,590
But now, that's impossible.

153
00:07:53,860 --> 00:07:55,460
A person must honor their promises.

154
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:58,100
If I hadn't promised Ms. Jian,

155
00:07:58,100 --> 00:08:00,220
I would've stayed far away from this.

156
00:08:00,220 --> 00:08:02,190
It would've had nothing to do with me.

157
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:04,830
But now, I have to help the company

158
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:06,330
get through this critical period.

159
00:08:06,830 --> 00:08:08,630
Once the company is back on track,

160
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:10,190
if you think I'm not capable enough,

161
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:12,520
and not qualified to take this position,

162
00:08:13,030 --> 00:08:14,300
I can leave anytime.

163
00:08:18,510 --> 00:08:19,780
Nice words.

164
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:22,780
But can you keep your word?

165
00:08:23,070 --> 00:08:23,910
Of course.

166
00:08:24,390 --> 00:08:25,540
I always keep my word.

167
00:08:26,510 --> 00:08:27,780
But before that,

168
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:31,100
I hope everyone will cooperate with me.

169
00:08:31,710 --> 00:08:33,420
I've said almost everything I need to.

170
00:08:33,660 --> 00:08:35,420
I came here today for this meal,

171
00:08:35,420 --> 00:08:37,030
not to make enemies with anyone.

172
00:08:37,390 --> 00:08:40,540
I know you all are seniors at the company

173
00:08:40,900 --> 00:08:42,510
and have your own ways of doing things.

174
00:08:42,820 --> 00:08:45,700
Do whatever you wish.

175
00:08:46,300 --> 00:08:47,390
I, Zhao Chuxi,

176
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:48,750
will face it head-on.

177
00:09:05,300 --> 00:09:06,140
Come on.

178
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:08,030
I propose a toast to you.

179
00:09:35,900 --> 00:09:36,740
Chuxi,

180
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:40,990
starting today, I'll leave the Board.

181
00:09:42,230 --> 00:09:45,750
Fan Li will take my place on the Board.

182
00:09:46,230 --> 00:09:48,870
I simultaneously resign from the Board

183
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:52,270
and step down as President of Sanjiang Group.

184
00:09:52,470 --> 00:09:55,800
I recommend Xu Lin, the Vice President,

185
00:09:56,060 --> 00:09:57,670
to take over as President of the Group.

186
00:09:57,670 --> 00:09:58,700
(Sanjiang Group)

187
00:09:58,700 --> 00:09:59,540
Mr. Du,

188
00:09:59,630 --> 00:10:00,870
there's no need for this.

189
00:10:00,870 --> 00:10:02,700
I've been planning this for a while.

190
00:10:02,700 --> 00:10:04,110
I just didn't discuss it with you.

191
00:10:05,030 --> 00:10:07,510
Xu Lin's presence reassures me

192
00:10:07,510 --> 00:10:09,510
I can leave without worry.

193
00:10:11,030 --> 00:10:12,700
Since that's the case,

194
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:15,870
the company's last Board seat

195
00:10:16,420 --> 00:10:17,620
will be given to Zhang Chao.

196
00:10:18,110 --> 00:10:19,230
This is just an exchange.

197
00:10:19,230 --> 00:10:21,350
It's not about repaying a favor.

198
00:10:24,110 --> 00:10:26,230
I didn't expect this outcome either.

199
00:10:27,060 --> 00:10:29,660
Perhaps no one did.

200
00:10:30,540 --> 00:10:31,750
You don't need to thank me.

201
00:10:32,030 --> 00:10:33,230
This is what you deserve.

202
00:10:33,230 --> 00:10:37,030
Mr. Du, did you decide
to support me early on,

203
00:10:37,510 --> 00:10:39,060
or was it a last-minute decision?

204
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:40,300
What do you think?

205
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:44,180
I believe I understand now.

206
00:10:44,990 --> 00:10:46,060
But, Mr. Du,

207
00:10:46,470 --> 00:10:49,060
you've offended everyone

208
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:51,300
to help me take over Sanjiang Group.

209
00:10:53,230 --> 00:10:55,350
I spent 50 years of life in vain.

210
00:10:56,060 --> 00:10:57,230
Over a decade ago,

211
00:10:57,750 --> 00:10:59,060
if it weren't for Ms. Jian,

212
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:02,420
my life would be worlds apart.

213
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:04,700
Shouldn't I already be content?

214
00:11:05,150 --> 00:11:06,840
As for their intentions

215
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,110
and the schemes they might have

216
00:11:08,110 --> 00:11:09,350
with Sanjiang Group,

217
00:11:09,350 --> 00:11:11,030
how could I not be aware?

218
00:11:12,030 --> 00:11:15,660
Sanjiang Group is the result of my hard work.

219
00:11:16,010 --> 00:11:18,730
How could I let them destroy it?

220
00:11:19,470 --> 00:11:20,660
They're watching you.

221
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:22,420
And so am I.

222
00:11:23,060 --> 00:11:25,230
Ms. Jian is watching you too.

223
00:11:25,710 --> 00:11:27,400
I don't know you well enough.

224
00:11:27,410 --> 00:11:28,820
What kind of person are you?

225
00:11:29,040 --> 00:11:31,630
Do you have the ability to control the Group?

226
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:35,180
Can you battle with these big players?

227
00:11:35,730 --> 00:11:37,680
I need to observe step by step.

228
00:11:37,870 --> 00:11:39,350
It's also a test for you.

229
00:11:39,660 --> 00:11:42,660
If I revealed myself right from the start,

230
00:11:43,030 --> 00:11:46,150
wouldn't that be too easy for you?

231
00:11:46,350 --> 00:11:47,700
No pressure at all.

232
00:11:48,630 --> 00:11:49,580
I can see clearly.

233
00:11:49,580 --> 00:11:52,700
Xu Lin, Song Qingci, Furong and Huang Tu

234
00:11:53,230 --> 00:11:54,940
all have great trust in you.

235
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:57,870
Gaining their trust itself

236
00:11:58,420 --> 00:12:01,230
shows your capability.

237
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:02,310
Mr. Du,

238
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:04,470
no matter what,

239
00:12:05,210 --> 00:12:08,230
I truly hope you'll stay and help me.

240
00:12:09,470 --> 00:12:11,700
Xu Lin is more capable than I am.

241
00:12:12,660 --> 00:12:16,350
Sanjiang Group will have a brighter future.

242
00:12:17,060 --> 00:12:19,470
I'm already exhausted.

243
00:12:19,660 --> 00:12:20,630
All these years,

244
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:23,030
I barely had time for my family.

245
00:12:23,540 --> 00:12:26,900
It's time for us to enjoy some peace.

246
00:12:29,540 --> 00:12:30,580
Alright, Mr. Du.

247
00:12:31,300 --> 00:12:33,230
Since you've made up your mind,

248
00:12:33,900 --> 00:12:35,350
I won't try to stop you.

249
00:12:35,830 --> 00:12:36,700
Okay.

250
00:12:36,700 --> 00:12:38,870
I wish you good health,

251
00:12:39,230 --> 00:12:40,820
and happiness with your family.

252
00:12:40,820 --> 00:12:42,660
Let's all keep doing our best.

253
00:12:45,540 --> 00:12:46,380
Here, Mr. Du.

254
00:12:50,540 --> 00:12:51,480
Take care on your way.

255
00:12:57,990 --> 00:12:58,830
Qingyi,

256
00:12:59,060 --> 00:13:00,580
we bought so many new clothes

257
00:13:00,940 --> 00:13:02,450
and so many school supplies this time.

258
00:13:02,510 --> 00:13:04,300
This is enough for two or three months.

259
00:13:04,300 --> 00:13:05,170
Yes,

260
00:13:05,180 --> 00:13:06,540
it should be enough for a while.

261
00:13:07,060 --> 00:13:09,300
I'll come out again before the heavy snow.

262
00:13:10,030 --> 00:13:12,700
Otherwise, we'll have to wait
until winter ends.

263
00:13:13,630 --> 00:13:14,480
Hei,

264
00:13:14,580 --> 00:13:15,840
thanks for helping me this time.

265
00:13:15,870 --> 00:13:16,850
You're welcome, Qingyi.

266
00:13:17,110 --> 00:13:18,820
The snow is so heavy these days.

267
00:13:19,230 --> 00:13:21,300
If I didn't come with you, it'd be too risky.

268
00:13:21,300 --> 00:13:22,530
Accidents could easily happen.

269
00:13:26,630 --> 00:13:27,510
What's wrong, Qingyi?

270
00:13:29,990 --> 00:13:31,180
I don't know why,

271
00:13:32,030 --> 00:13:33,490
but I feel a tightness in my chest.

272
00:13:34,590 --> 00:13:36,620
And my right eyelid keeps twitching.

273
00:13:38,630 --> 00:13:40,030
Could you have caught a cold?

274
00:13:40,340 --> 00:13:41,750
Why don't you hold on a bit longer?

275
00:13:41,750 --> 00:13:42,900
We'll be in the village soon.

276
00:13:42,900 --> 00:13:44,470
I'll make you some herbal soup.

277
00:13:44,630 --> 00:13:45,470
I'm fine.

278
00:13:45,700 --> 00:13:47,060
I'll be better soon. Let's go.

279
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:52,470
Take it slow, Qingyi.

280
00:13:56,350 --> 00:13:57,300
Chuxi,

281
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:58,780
Mr. Du really resigned?

282
00:13:59,310 --> 00:14:00,580
