285
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:06,630
I guess he has his own plans.

286
00:14:08,770 --> 00:14:11,060
Sanjiang Group will depend on you now.

287
00:14:15,180 --> 00:14:16,020
Qingci.

288
00:14:24,230 --> 00:14:25,070
