289
00:14:25,350 --> 00:14:27,350
This is this month's financial report.

290
00:14:27,470 --> 00:14:29,630
Some departments performed quite well.

291
00:14:31,470 --> 00:14:33,870
Here's the latest legal regulations.

292
00:14:33,870 --> 00:14:35,300
I think you should review them.

293
00:14:35,300 --> 00:14:36,420
If everything goes well,

294
00:14:36,420 --> 00:14:38,630
the Jiatou's shares should be finalized soon.

295
00:14:38,630 --> 00:14:40,510
This is one of Aunt Jian's trump cards.

296
00:14:40,730 --> 00:14:42,470
We need to act discreetly

297
00:14:42,470 --> 00:14:44,350
to catch those old guys off guard.

298
00:14:44,870 --> 00:14:45,870
Understood, Mr. Zhao.

299
00:14:46,270 --> 00:14:49,420
You need to attend a few banquets next month.

300
00:14:49,940 --> 00:14:52,750
Aunt Jian used to handle these events.

301
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:54,470
But now Aunt Jian is gone.

302
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:56,230
It's also the critical moment.

303
00:14:56,940 --> 00:14:58,540
Your presence is even more crucial now.

304
00:14:58,540 --> 00:15:00,150
You need to send a message to the public

305
00:15:00,420 --> 00:15:02,940
that Sanjiang has transitioned leadership.

306
00:15:03,470 --> 00:15:05,230
Sanjiang Group remains the same as before.

307
00:15:05,420 --> 00:15:07,940
But now, it's the era of Zhao Chuxi.

308
00:15:08,060 --> 00:15:08,900
Mr. Zhao!

309
00:15:10,660 --> 00:15:12,070
Something bad happened!

310
00:15:12,794 --> 00:15:13,220
What is it?

311
00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:15,540
He Yuanshan is holding a press conference.

312
00:15:16,030 --> 00:15:18,470
He wants to make the subsidiary independent.

313
00:15:21,030 --> 00:15:22,150
I hereby announce,

314
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:25,470
I'm withdrawing from the Board.

315
00:15:26,150 --> 00:15:29,230
(Sanjiang Group's director withdraws)
Also, the subsidiary I was managing

316
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:30,870
(Subsidiary declares independence)
is officially declaring independence.

317
00:15:30,870 --> 00:15:33,820
Both Wu Heping and Chen Tao

318
00:15:33,820 --> 00:15:36,580
have also decided to withdraw from the Board.

319
00:15:38,550 --> 00:15:39,810
Please share more with us.

320
00:15:40,180 --> 00:15:41,510
