324
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:51,630
Mr. Du had a car accident in Jiangbei.

325
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:52,660
When did it happen?

326
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:53,870
Just now.

327
00:15:54,030 --> 00:15:56,150
He is in the hospital, fighting for his life.

328
00:15:56,150 --> 00:15:57,210
Let's go. To the hospital.

329
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:04,180
Those are just rumors.

330
00:16:11,470 --> 00:16:12,310
Furong,

331
00:16:12,700 --> 00:16:16,230
