332
00:16:16,350 --> 00:16:17,300
I think so too.

333
00:16:17,300 --> 00:16:20,660
Let's wait till we reach Jiangbei to confirm.

334
00:16:20,660 --> 00:16:23,110
Only He Yuanshan would dare to do this.

335
00:16:23,300 --> 00:16:25,030
No one else has that kind of power.

336
00:16:25,540 --> 00:16:26,630
But we can't be certain.

337
00:16:27,940 --> 00:16:29,470
