339
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:47,590
Watch out!

340
00:16:56,110 --> 00:16:57,540
- Hei.
- Qingyi.

341
00:16:57,540 --> 00:16:58,750
Have you noticed

342
00:16:59,270 --> 00:17:00,870
how fluffy the snow is this year?

343
00:17:03,300 --> 00:17:04,300
Yeah, it's fluffy.

344
00:17:05,140 --> 00:17:06,470
This weight is really crushing.

345
00:17:06,470 --> 00:17:07,310
Exactly.

346
00:17:07,670 --> 00:17:09,950
Let's go. My feet are freezing.

347
00:17:16,820 --> 00:17:18,230
The village...

348
00:17:18,620 --> 00:17:19,460
It's gone.

349
00:17:27,300 --> 00:17:28,230
Father!

350
00:17:28,950 --> 00:17:29,820
Mother!

351
00:17:33,860 --> 00:17:36,510
Father! Mother!

352
00:17:55,060 --> 00:17:55,900
Chuxi...

353
00:17:56,140 --> 00:17:56,980
Chuxi...

354
00:17:57,470 --> 00:17:58,310
- Furong!
- Furong!

355
00:17:58,820 --> 00:17:59,930
- Are you okay?
- Huang Tu!

356
00:18:00,190 --> 00:18:01,030
Huang Tu!

357
00:18:01,470 --> 00:18:02,470
Chuxi, what's wrong?

358
00:18:02,470 --> 00:18:04,030
- Chuxi!
- What's wrong?

359
00:18:04,710 --> 00:18:05,550
Chuxi!

360
00:18:05,780 --> 00:18:06,620
Chuxi...

361
00:18:30,670 --> 00:18:31,510
Ms. Li.

362
00:18:33,300 --> 00:18:34,380
Mr. Li.

363
00:18:46,860 --> 00:18:47,710
Mr. Li.

364
00:19:04,750 --> 00:19:06,270
Mr. Li, Mr. Li!

365
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:07,820
You're finally back.

366
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:09,030
Mr. Li.

367
00:19:09,710 --> 00:19:11,750
- Mr. Li.
- Mr. Li.

368
00:19:24,140 --> 00:19:24,990
Mr. Li,

369
00:19:25,990 --> 00:19:27,340
you're finally back.

370
00:19:27,580 --> 00:19:30,470
The heavy snow collapsed houses.

371
00:19:30,580 --> 00:19:32,510
To protect

372
00:19:33,060 --> 00:19:34,300
and evacuate the villagers,

373
00:19:36,580 --> 00:19:37,540
the village chief...

374
00:19:48,380 --> 00:19:49,580
The village chief...

375
00:19:53,470 --> 00:19:54,780
I'm back.

376
00:19:55,470 --> 00:19:56,670
I'm back.

377
00:19:59,100 --> 00:20:06,100
(Phoenix Village Elementary School)

378
00:20:13,540 --> 00:20:14,710
You don't need to see me off.

379
00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:16,380
Go back now.

380
00:20:16,950 --> 00:20:19,540
Mr. Li, will you return again?

381
00:20:20,430 --> 00:20:22,540
Mr. Li, when will you come back?

382
00:20:23,580 --> 00:20:25,140
Of course I'll be back.

383
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:27,820
I still need to teach you all.

384
00:20:34,190 --> 00:20:35,950
Phoenix Village has been submerged,

385
00:20:37,430 --> 00:20:38,950
but as long as we are alive,

386
00:20:39,710 --> 00:20:41,230
a new Phoenix Village will rise.

387
00:20:41,510 --> 00:20:44,100
Yes, as long as we are here, there is hope.

388
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:46,030
Yes, yes, that's right.

389
00:20:55,910 --> 00:20:57,370
I will definitely come back someday.

390
00:21:07,430 --> 00:21:09,030
(The mountains are still the same.)

391
00:21:09,780 --> 00:21:13,470
(But Phoenix Village is no longer there.)

392
00:21:14,340 --> 00:21:15,300
(At this moment,)

393
00:21:15,470 --> 00:21:18,670
(Li Qingyi, who has persevered for years,)

394
00:21:18,950 --> 00:21:21,340
(is finally leaving Phoenix Village.)

395
00:21:21,860 --> 00:21:25,580
(Yet the way of leaving feels almost heroic.)

396
00:21:26,670 --> 00:21:29,380
(Dust returns to dust, soil returns to soil.)

397
00:21:29,990 --> 00:21:32,140
(Everything has finally come to rest.)

398
00:21:33,340 --> 00:21:35,580
(The elementary school still remains.)

399
00:21:36,140 --> 00:21:38,280
(The graves beside the school still stand.)

400
00:21:38,280 --> 00:21:39,670
(Phoenix Village Elementary School)

401
00:21:39,670 --> 00:21:40,670
(There lies Ping'an,)

402
00:21:40,840 --> 00:21:42,430
(who never saw what a big city was like)

403
00:21:42,430 --> 00:21:44,820
(even at the moment of death;)

404
00:21:45,340 --> 00:21:48,380
(there lies the mother of Zhao Chuxi;)

405
00:21:48,860 --> 00:21:50,670
(there lies the father of Zhao Chuxi;)

406
00:21:50,990 --> 00:21:52,380
(there lies the old principal;)

407
00:21:52,860 --> 00:21:55,430
(there lies the village chief who died)

408
00:21:55,950 --> 00:21:58,340
(while organizing the evacuation.)

409
00:21:59,860 --> 00:22:01,270
Who could possibly do this?

410
00:22:02,340 --> 00:22:03,950
If it's not He Yuanshan,

411
00:22:04,860 --> 00:22:06,330
I truly can't think of anyone else.

412
00:22:13,300 --> 00:22:15,750
Both He Yuanshan and Wu Heping are suspects.

413
00:22:19,300 --> 00:22:20,990
By the way, how is Mr. Du?

414
00:22:23,780 --> 00:22:26,670
He will be bedridden for the rest of my life.

415
00:22:32,710 --> 00:22:34,300
They are warning me.

416
00:22:39,140 --> 00:22:39,980
Chuxi,

417
00:22:40,380 --> 00:22:41,220
what do we do now?

418
00:22:42,540 --> 00:22:44,090
(At this moment, Zhao Chuxi realizes)

419
00:22:44,710 --> 00:22:46,990
(he had oversimplified the situation.)

420
00:22:47,510 --> 00:22:49,270
(His actions now)

421
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:51,380
(are indeed affecting others.)

422
00:22:52,190 --> 00:22:54,140
(This isn't a little money.)

423
00:22:54,820 --> 00:22:56,380
(He hesitated for a moment.)

424
00:22:56,750 --> 00:22:58,950
(Was this choice right or wrong?)

425
00:22:59,300 --> 00:23:01,190
(A promise is simple.)

426
00:23:01,540 --> 00:23:04,950
(But it could implicate himself and others.)

427
00:23:05,230 --> 00:23:08,230
(Or perhaps it requires a heavy price.)

428
00:23:08,500 --> 00:23:12,620
(Yujing Longcheng)

429
00:23:17,030 --> 00:23:17,910
Who are you?

430
00:23:18,820 --> 00:23:20,030
I'm Li Qingyi.

431
00:23:20,230 --> 00:23:21,540
I'm here to see Zhao Chuxi.

432
00:23:23,340 --> 00:23:24,180
Wait a moment.

433
00:23:30,950 --> 00:23:31,790
Zhao,

434
00:23:31,950 --> 00:23:32,990
someone's here to see you.

435
00:23:33,020 --> 00:23:33,860
Who is it?

436
00:23:33,860 --> 00:23:35,820
She says her name is Li Qingyi.

437
00:23:49,620 --> 00:23:50,460
Sis,

438
00:23:50,950 --> 00:23:52,270
why are you here?

439
00:23:57,540 --> 00:23:58,380
What happened?

440
00:23:59,750 --> 00:24:01,140
Did you hear something?

441
00:24:02,710 --> 00:24:03,710
I'm fine here.

442
00:24:03,710 --> 00:24:05,430
It's just a minor injury, look.

443
00:24:05,750 --> 00:24:07,470
I'm perfectly fine, arms and legs intact.

444
00:24:07,820 --> 00:24:09,190
You don't need to worry about me.

445
00:24:19,380 --> 00:24:21,620
Are you worried that I'm doing better now

446
00:24:21,620 --> 00:24:23,060
and I'll forget where I came from?

447
00:24:23,380 --> 00:24:25,380
No worries. I promised

448
00:24:25,380 --> 00:24:26,880
to build a school and pave the roads,

449
00:24:27,140 --> 00:24:29,440
make the surrounding villages envy us

450
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:30,810
and bring honor to Phoenix Village.

451
00:24:30,810 --> 00:24:32,230
I'll definitely make it happen.

452
00:24:33,300 --> 00:24:34,270
Absolutely.

453
00:24:40,510 --> 00:24:42,230
What's wrong? Say something!

454
00:24:44,950 --> 00:24:45,860
The village is gone.

455
00:24:46,780 --> 00:24:47,710
What's gone?

456
00:24:48,510 --> 00:24:49,820
Phoenix Village is gone.

457
00:24:53,230 --> 00:24:54,100
Gone...

458
00:24:57,820 --> 00:24:58,820
The snow was too heavy.

459
00:24:59,910 --> 00:25:01,580
The village houses collapsed.

460
00:25:02,540 --> 00:25:03,750
To protect everyone,

461
00:25:04,780 --> 00:25:06,360
the old village chief

462
00:25:09,340 --> 00:25:10,180
didn't come out.

463
00:25:18,910 --> 00:25:19,820
Didn't come out...

464
00:25:22,140 --> 00:25:23,190
Didn't come out...

465
00:25:23,300 --> 00:25:24,620
Didn't come out...

466
00:25:28,710 --> 00:25:29,750
Gone...

467
00:25:29,910 --> 00:25:31,750
Didn't come out...

468
00:25:32,750 --> 00:25:33,590
Gone...

469
00:27:04,380 --> 00:27:06,750
I'll go out and make money soon.

470
00:27:07,230 --> 00:27:08,910
Who will you listen to when I'm not here?

471
00:27:09,230 --> 00:27:10,990
Listen to Ms. Li.

472
00:27:32,540 --> 00:27:33,620
Go check on him.

473
00:27:35,750 --> 00:27:37,230
Let him be alone for a while.

474
00:27:44,060 --> 00:27:44,950
I'm going for a smoke.

475
00:27:52,380 --> 00:27:53,220
I'll go too.

476
00:28:08,910 --> 00:28:10,580
Something's wrong! Chuxi is missing!

477
00:28:12,030 --> 00:28:14,670
Where could he go alone at this time?

478
00:28:15,470 --> 00:28:17,140
- Phoenix Village?
- Impossible.

479
00:28:17,710 --> 00:28:19,540
Anywhere is possible, but not that village.

480
00:28:19,660 --> 00:28:20,510
Why not?

481
00:28:20,510 --> 00:28:23,060
He said he wouldn't return without success.

482
00:28:24,300 --> 00:28:25,510
In his current state,

483
00:28:25,510 --> 00:28:26,990
he won't return to Phoenix Village.

484
00:28:29,670 --> 00:28:31,060
What exactly is he planning to do?

485
00:28:31,270 --> 00:28:33,130
He's abandoned such a massive responsibility.

486
00:28:33,140 --> 00:28:34,510
What does he want the group to do?

487
00:28:34,910 --> 00:28:35,750
Furong.

488
00:28:37,540 --> 00:28:40,470
Phoenix Village is like Chuxi's lifeblood.

489
00:28:40,780 --> 00:28:42,860
Why did he leave for the city back then?

490
00:28:43,750 --> 00:28:44,950
Now the village is gone.

491
00:28:45,540 --> 00:28:48,190
It's like Chuxi has lost his foundation.

492
00:28:48,860 --> 00:28:51,270
Aunt Jian trusted Chuxi with the group.

493
00:28:51,750 --> 00:28:53,620
I believe Chuxi knows what he's doing.

494
00:28:54,030 --> 00:28:55,340
Right now, in the group,

495
00:28:55,340 --> 00:28:57,270
we have Mr. Xu and Qingci.

496
00:28:57,430 --> 00:28:59,860
The rest is up to us to handle.

497
00:29:01,540 --> 00:29:02,540
No matter what,

498
00:29:02,860 --> 00:29:04,100
we must find Chuxi.

499
00:29:04,540 --> 00:29:05,710
If we truly can't find him,

500
00:29:05,710 --> 00:29:06,980
we'll wait for him to come back.

501
00:29:06,980 --> 00:29:08,030
No need to search for him.

502
00:29:08,580 --> 00:29:09,670
If he wants to leave,

503
00:29:10,340 --> 00:29:11,470
no one can bring him back.

504
00:29:12,190 --> 00:29:15,430
I think as long as Chuxi hasn't fallen,

505
00:29:16,060 --> 00:29:17,190
there's still hope.

506
00:29:47,700 --> 00:29:54,460
(One week later)

507
00:29:59,230 --> 00:30:00,070
Chuxi,

508
00:30:00,710 --> 00:30:01,580
life is all

509
