515
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:23,030
My parents and Ping'an

516
00:30:23,620 --> 00:30:26,270
wouldn't have died because of heavy snow.

517
00:30:26,670 --> 00:30:28,430
And Dad wouldn't have missed treatment

518
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:31,300
(Tomb of Mother Li Xiuzhu and Father Li Chengqian)
due to being trapped by snow.

519
00:30:31,300 --> 00:30:32,140
You said,

520
00:30:32,580 --> 00:30:34,860
that's the place Dad swore to protect,

521
00:30:34,860 --> 00:30:36,540
so you have to guard it too.

522
00:30:36,910 --> 00:30:39,820
You leave here for now because you want

523
00:30:40,380 --> 00:30:43,230
to make money to improve the village.

524
00:30:46,470 --> 00:30:47,510
I should go now.

525
00:30:49,100 --> 00:30:51,060
I'll visit you every year.

526
00:30:52,750 --> 00:30:53,590
Don't worry.

527
00:30:54,510 --> 00:30:56,140
I know what I need to do.

528
00:30:56,620 --> 00:30:57,750
I've figured it out.

529
00:31:00,140 --> 00:31:01,580
I won't let them take me down.

530
00:31:02,910 --> 00:31:04,140
Just like you said,

531
00:31:05,580 --> 00:31:09,430
I'll overcome these obstacles one by one.

532
00:31:10,860 --> 00:31:13,820
