I'll move forward firmly.

533
00:31:32,270 --> 00:31:34,470
Sir, show me your ticket, please.

534
00:31:41,030 --> 00:31:42,910
Train K1394.

535
00:31:42,910 --> 00:31:44,620
Please pay attention to your stop.

536
00:31:44,620 --> 00:31:46,100
- Have a chat, miss?
- Sir,

537
00:31:46,100 --> 00:31:47,380
please mind your behavior.

538
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:48,750
Don't be so uptight.

539
00:31:48,750 --> 00:31:51,100
Let's grab a meal and chat together.

540
00:31:51,230 --> 00:31:52,230
Get to know each other.

541
00:31:52,670 --> 00:31:53,700
(Book of the Later Han)
I

542
00:31:53,700 --> 00:31:56,710
do have some influence in Sanjiang.

543
00:31:56,910 --> 00:31:58,060
Sorry, sir.

544
00:31:58,340 --> 00:31:59,300
We have a policy.

545
00:31:59,470 --> 00:32:01,430
Meeting passengers privately is not allowed.

546
00:32:01,430 --> 00:32:02,780
If that's your attitude,

547
00:32:02,780 --> 00:32:03,950
I'll have to complain you.

548
00:32:03,950 --> 00:32:04,790
Do as you please.

549
00:32:05,030 --> 00:32:06,950
I'm inviting you to dinner out of courtesy.

550
00:32:06,950 --> 00:32:08,340
Don't push your luck.

